    <CompAttribute name="allChildValues" id="1fb77900-cea8-42c9-a191-88c7703f07d7">
        <type name="IntegerArray"/>
        <text>

These are all the modules the permission is in.
These permissions are build from the global constant XML in the text of the constant.

There is a children section. The children are the global constnat value of the module minus the value of PmAdmBaseView (10635)

Any permission value &gt;= PmAdmBaseView is a module.

In 2019 the modules were refactored so the global constant XML chidlren might have a value for a module that does not exist anymore.</text>
    </CompAttribute>
